title: Making strides for greater mental health (Government of British Columbia)
text: ( Source : Government of British Columbia ) VICTORIA - Health Minister Terry Lake has issued the following statement today to recognize Oct. 10 , 2015 , as World Mental Health Day , and the week of Oct. 4-10, 2015, as Mental Illness Awareness
